{"tid":1176572,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【投資七位數】可嵐開舖寓工作於娛樂 魏駿傑唔介意做變態佬","createTime":"2019-05-29T09:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T10:26:07.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"663dc2bc7dc9bd3903f447472421f1e7f65b7196","tid":1176572,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T09:59:53.000Z","msg":"魏駿傑、林雅詩及布偉傑夫婦，今日去到錦田出席可嵐經營的糖水店開幕禮，老闆娘可嵐透露今次開舖是無心插柳，全因自己住在附近，閒時會煲湯水及糖水請街坊及店舖老闆飲，有次剛巧這間茶餐廳老闆吃過糖水後，便提議茶餐廳每日收舖後，改為糖水店，可嵐經深思熟慮後接受提議，並投資七位數，她說：「已經試業咗個幾月，以港式糖水為主，我不停鑽研古早味紅荳沙，都有一定心得。」<br />\n鄰近屋企，可嵐指囝囝也經常到店內，或者因她前夫是經營飲食業，囝囝對茶餐廳有份感情，今次開店囝囝都非常開心。糖水店亦化身為可嵐busking埸地，差不多半個月便舉行一場，吸引不少捧場客，她表示可以寓工作於娛樂，問到現在有沒有追求者？她說：「有，但首位係放囝囝先，之後係努力賺錢，我一個女人仔賺錢能力唔高，要付出二百分努力先得。」<br />\n魏駿傑表示跟其中一位老闆是老友，因此到賀。本身也有經營飲食生意的他，指生意主要在大陸市場發展，原先計劃間中客串拍戲等退休的他又透露，最近拍了一套內地電影《夢醒黃金城》，會在稍後上映：「拍完令我好有信心，雖然自己知道年紀大同福相咗，但部戲宣傳片喺抖音一星期有700萬點擊。」<br />\n今次亦令不少人記起魏駿傑幕前演出，他指酬勞是次要，接拍與否取決於劇本是否吸引，最重要是演未做過的角色，演變態佬或反派都可以。至於問到香港市場，他笑說：「我想返香港，但係時勢唔同咗，我都係安心喺內地發展，始終市場大啲。不過我同大台好似仲有一部劇嘅約要拍，再等佢聯絡我啦。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190529/large/1559113894_10f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190529%2Flarge%2F1559113894_10f8.jpg&h=df8986f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190529/large/1559113894_60ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190529%2Flarge%2F1559113894_60ed.jpg&h=cdb6493d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190529/large/1559113894_c465.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190529%2Flarge%2F1559113894_c465.jpg&h=1fe716ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190529/large/1559113896_428a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190529%2Flarge%2F1559113896_428a.jpg&h=3a8e3dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190529/large/1559113897_58a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190529%2Flarge%2F1559113897_58a9.jpg&h=6986b41d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190529/59654079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190529%2F59654079&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=fba2367c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190529%2F59654079&h=39995cb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190529/59654079</a>"},{"pid":"7cc5a63d97809ced2bb956211a6009a6ab46f974","tid":1176572,"uid":152123,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:07:00.000Z","msg":"暗星大聯盟"},{"pid":"50f6475a45ab60bb428fe2ed7ccc20f4ca73f084","tid":1176572,"uid":49267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"魏生個肚腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b1055293367ec1a9b730b89c96e811f20f8b6a","tid":1176572,"uid":31060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:38:51.000Z","msg":"糖水鋪?七位數?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e7e80c946ffa4e6c67a111cece2612a2fdbcf6","tid":1176572,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50f6475a45ab60bb428fe2ed7ccc20f4ca73f084","tid":1176572,"uid":49267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"魏生個肚腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa